# 🎌 Anime Search App

A modern React application to search and explore anime, powered by the [Jikan API](https://docs.api.jikan.moe/). Features instant search, server-side pagination, detailed anime view, and a clean UI built with Material UI.

## ✨ Features

- 🔍 Instant search with debounce (250ms)
- 📄 Server-side pagination
- 🖼️ Anime detail pages with full info
- 💅 Responsive and aesthetic UI (MUI)
- ⚡ Data fetching with TanStack Query
- 🔁 Custom hooks for fetching logic
- 🧪 Graceful handling of loading, empty state, and errors
- 💥 Handles race conditions when typing quickly

## 🚀 Technologies Used

- React
- React Router DOM
- @mui/material (Material UI)
- @mui/icons-material
- @tanstack/react-query
- Axios
- Jikan API v4

## 📦 Installation

1. **Clone the repo**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/anime-search-app.git
   cd anime-search-app

   ```
2. **Install dependencies**

   ```bash
   npm install

   ```

3. **Run the app**
   ```bash
   git npm start
   ```
